    Alle Klassen und Schnittstellen

    Klasse
    Beschreibung
    API
    Handles all API requests to fetch drone data.
    AppException
    Custom runtime exception for application-specific errors.
    ChartUtils
    Utility class to create different types of charts for the GUI.
    ConfigPanel
    ConfigPanel allows the user to enter API URL and token before accessing the application.
    Constants
    Holds global constants used for API connection.
    DashboardPanel
    DashboardPanel displays an overview of all drones and charts with aggregated data.
    DataAggregator
    Provides helper methods to compute aggregated drone data.
    DataRepository
    Singleton class that stores and provides access to drone data.
    Drone
    Represents a single drone with static properties.
    DroneCatalogPanel
    DroneCatalogPanel displays all drone types and shows drones of a selected type.
    DroneDynamics
    Represents real-time dynamic data of a drone.
    DroneFilter
    Provides simple filters for drone data.
    DroneType
    Represents a drone model with its technical specifications.
    FlightDynamicsPanel
    Panel to display drone flight dynamics with pagination and Google Maps integration.
    HomePanel
    HomePanel shows the welcome screen with navigation buttons.
    IDataProvider
    Interface for providing access to drone-related data.
    Main
    Main class to start the application.
    MainFrame
    MainFrame is the main window of the application.
    StyleUtil
    Utility class for styling and layout helpers used in the GUI.
